Bring all your beach memories to fruition in your bathroom with this Coastal Collage bath ensemble. Each piece perfectly represents beach fun with iconic colors of aqua, seafoam green and sand. Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.

transcripts: The coastal collage back ensemble will bring back all your beach memories. Each piece of the ensemble perfectly represents beach fun with iconic colors of aqua sea foam green and sand. The ensemble includes a lotion dispenser and wastebasket toothbrush holder soap dish tumbler and tissue holder. The coastal ball is available at bed bath and beyond.
